 Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above.JOHANNESBURG - The Nelson Mandela Foundation and the Ahmed Kathrada Foundation held a prayer service for the late Ahmed Kathrada on Tuesday morning.Kathrada passed away at the Donald Gordon Hospital in Johannesburg after a short illness.The prayer service will be held at the offices of Nelson Mandela Foundation in Houghton.The Mandela Foundation urged mourners to post their messages of condolence in either video or text format with on social media using #Kathrada.People who have pictures with the struggle stalwart were also encouraged to post them."The messages will be delivered to the family of Mr Kathrada," the Nelson Mandela Foundation said.Tweets about #Kathrada AND(FROM:@nzimandebafana since:2017-03-28) eNCA